	(&_deprecated): Skip deprecated element checks in XML mode.
	
	* README:
	Corrected requirements (HTML::Tagset _is_ needed).
	
	* README, bin/gmuck.pod, lib/HTML/GMUCK.pod:
	Copyright and URL tuning.

	* t/008tabwidth.t: New file.

